sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as UE
    participant M as Middleware
    participant DB as Middleware<br/>SQLite buffer
    participant B as Backend
    participant PG as PostgreSQL

    Note over U,PG: match_completed with idempotency + offline buffer

    Note over U: Player just finished Level 1

    U->>U: Generate idempotency key:<br/>"sess_abc-L1-A1" (sessionId + level + attempt)
    U--)M: match_completed payload

    M->>DB: INSERT INTO pending_events<br/>(idempotency_key, payload, attempts=0)

    alt Backend online
        M->>B: POST /sessions/{id}/matches<br/>Header: Idempotency-Key: sess_abc-L1-A1

        alt First time (not seen before)
            B->>PG: BEGIN
            B->>PG: SELECT match WHERE idempotency_key=?
            Note over B: row not found
            B->>PG: INSERT Match (level=1, score=1920, ...)
            B->>PG: COMMIT
            B-->>M: 201 Created {matchId, created: true}
            M->>DB: UPDATE pending_events SET sent_at=NOW()
        else Duplicate request (e.g. retry after network glitch)
            B->>PG: SELECT match WHERE idempotency_key=?
            Note over B: row EXISTS
            B-->>M: 200 OK {matchId (existing), created: false}
            M->>DB: UPDATE pending_events SET sent_at=NOW()
        end

    else Backend offline / 5xx error
        B-->>M: Network timeout OR 503
        M->>DB: UPDATE pending_events SET attempts+=1, last_attempt_at=NOW()
        Note over M: wait backoff (1s, 2s, 4s, 8s...)

        loop Every 5 seconds
            M->>DB: SELECT pending_events WHERE sent_at IS NULL
            alt Events pending
                M->>B: Retry POST with same Idempotency-Key
                B->>PG: Check + INSERT or return existing
                B-->>M: 200 OK
                M->>DB: UPDATE sent_at=NOW()
            end
        end
    end

    Note over U,PG: Player continues playing Level 2 regardless<br/>(UE doesn't wait for backend ack)

    Note over M,B: Critical: match_completed is idempotent at backend level<br/>Duplicate send = no duplicate rating points
